      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Royal_Palm_Beach%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Every spring and fall, the village hosts food‑truck invasions, concerts, and movie nights projected onto inflatable screens, turning streets into pop‑up festivals.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
